st, I think we=E2=80=99re working on school bus size autonomous submarines =
( https://www.anduril.com/article/anduril-s-dive-xl-setting-new-standards-f=
or-maritime-autonomy/ ) , which are now swimming around, we=E2=80=99re work=
ing on autonomous fighter jets with the US Air Force ( https://www.anduril.=
com/article/anduril-air-force-collaborative-combat-aircraft-CCA/ ) , we=E2=
=80=99ve moved into missile programs, we=E2=80=99ve got a whole bunch of th=
ose going on. It=E2=80=99s really been a whole lot that has changed and the=
n on top of it, everything that=E2=80=99s happened with AI, how that=E2=80=
=99s infused what we do, all of those things have really shifted. So I feel=
 like the world has changed a lot in the last 16 months. And then, for Andu=
ril specifically, yeah, it feels like an entirely different company than la=
st time we talked.

