panies that are created, you end up having a view to what the future=E2=80=
=99s going to be, and if you=E2=80=99re right, you do well, and if you=E2=
=80=99re wrong, you go out of business, and nobody remembers who you were. =
I think the reality is, there=E2=80=99s no alternative, you just have to ac=
